name: AI-Powered Store Chatbot
description: An interactive AI-powered chatbot for an online store, built with React, TypeScript, and the Gemini API. This chatbot can provide information about products, payment methods, and shipping, and can have natural conversations with users. To add this code to a GitHub repository: 1. Create a new repository on GitHub.com. 2. In your local project folder, initialize Git with `git init`. 3. Add the remote repository URL: `git remote add origin <YOUR_GITHUB_REPO_URL>`. 4. Stage all files: `git add .`. 5. Commit the files: `git commit -m "Initial commit"`. 6. Push to GitHub: `git push -u origin main`.
